Interface MetaInformationInt

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdditionalCcAndBccCustomerInformation, MetaInformation, MetaInformationAnnotation, MetaInformationDesignerException, MetaInformationDocumentContainer, MetaInformationNotiz, MetaInformationOCRPage, MetaInformationOpenOffice, MetaInformationOriginalXML, MetaInformationTagmatch

    public interface MetaInformationInt
extends Cloneable
    interface for data that can be appended to an e-mail, such as tags, notes. In order for the attachments to be replaced in the documents.
